des:
Homgar Smart offers voice-controlled smart home experience with Alexa. Control your device hands free.

Here’s a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "HomGar" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on HomGar devices and connect them with “HomGar” app;
(4). IMPORTANT: You can rename the devices with HomGar App. So if you rename a power controller device “HomGar Power”, then Echo will get that same name after discovered the devices in Step 9;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(6). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "HomGar Smart";
(7). Click Enable skill of "HomGar Smart", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(8). Talk to Echo "Alexa,discover devices.". Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands HomGar Smart has:

Water Controller

Alexa, turn on the water controller
Alexa, turn off the water controller
Alexa, open water controller
Alexa, close water controller
